query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.name,
  p.brand,
  pc.categoryId,
  c.name as category_name
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
LEFT JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id
WHERE p.name LIKE '%Vial%'
LIMIT 20;
